---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Easy Squeeze Stainless Steel Wire Pegs — Gentle Grip for Sensitive Hands"
  description="Easy squeeze stainless steel wire pegs with a softer spring — perfect for arthritis, joint sensitivity, weak grip, or anyone who finds standard pegs too stiff. Available in Grade 201 and Grade 316."
>

  <section class="py-24 px-6 bg-navy-50">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
      <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-teal-500 mb-4">Specialty · Easy Squeeze</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-navy-900 leading-tight mb-6">Easy Squeeze Wire Pegs</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">All the durability of stainless steel wire — with a gentler spring that's kinder on your hands.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 px-6 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">

      <div class="bg-navy-50 rounded-2xl border border-navy-100 p-8 mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy-900 mb-6">Product specs</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-sm">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-4 border border-navy-100">
            <p class="text-navy-400 uppercase tracking-wider text-xs mb-1">Available Grades</p>
            <p class="font-semibold text-navy-900">201 or 316 Stainless Steel</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-4 border border-navy-100">
            <p class="text-navy-400 uppercase tracking-wider text-xs mb-1">Wire Diameter</p>
            <p class="font-semibold text-navy-900">1.5mm</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-4 border border-navy-100">
            <p class="text-navy-400 uppercase tracking-wider text-xs mb-1">Length</p>
            <p class="font-semibold text-navy-900">5.2cm</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-4 border border-navy-100">
            <p class="text-navy-400 uppercase tracking-wider text-xs mb-1">Pack Size</p>
            <p class="font-semibold text-navy-900">63 pegs in a hemp bag</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy-900 mb-4">A wire peg that's gentle on your hands</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">Standard wire pegs are built tough — which is great for holding washing on the line, but not so great if you have arthritis, joint sensitivity, reduced hand strength, or any condition that makes gripping and squeezing uncomfortable.</p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">Easy Squeeze pegs are made from thinner 1.5mm wire, which means a softer spring tension — roughly equivalent to a regular wooden or plastic peg. You get all the benefits of stainless steel (no rust, no breakage, no staining) with a grip that works with your hands, not against them.</p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">They come in packs of 63 in a reusable hemp bag — enough to handle a full load of washing with ease.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-navy-50 rounded-2xl p-8 mb-8 border border-navy-100">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy-900 mb-4">Perfect for</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600 text-sm">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-teal-500 font-bold">✓</span> Arthritis and joint pain in hands or fingers</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-teal-500 font-bold">✓</span> Reduced hand or finger strength</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-teal-500 font-bold">✓</span> Carpal tunnel or repetitive strain injury</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-teal-500 font-bold">✓</span> Older Australians who find standard pegs too stiff</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-teal-500 font-bold">✓</span> Anyone who prefers a lighter, easier grip</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-teal-500 font-bold">✓</span> Children helping with the laundry</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-teal-500 font-bold">✓</span> Those switching from plastic or wooden pegs who want a familiar feel</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-navy-50 rounded-2xl p-8 mb-8 border border-navy-100">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy-900 mb-4">Which grade should I choose?</h2>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-4 border border-navy-100">
            <p class="font-semibold text-navy-900 mb-1">Grade 201 — Standard</p>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Best for indoor use or if you bring your pegs inside after washing. Not suitable for coastal areas or leaving outside permanently.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-4 border border-navy-100">
            <p class="font-semibold text-navy-900 mb-1">Grade 316 — Marine Grade</p>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">The tougher option. Suitable for coastal homes, leaving pegs outside permanently, and harsh outdoor conditions. Will never rust.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mt-4">Not sure which grade is right for you? Use our <a href="/which-peg" class="text-teal-500 font-medium underline underline-offset-4">Peg Finder</a> for a personalised recommendation.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-navy-900 text-white rounded-2xl p-8 mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">A thoughtful gift idea</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm leading-relaxed">Easy Squeeze wire pegs make a genuinely useful gift for a parent, grandparent, or anyone who struggles with standard pegs. Packaged in a reusable hemp bag — no plastic packaging, no waste.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="text-center">
        <a href="https://www.biome.com.au/collections/wire-pegs" target="_blank" class="bg-teal-500 text-white font-semibold px-8 py-4 rounded-full hover:bg-teal-700 transition-colors text-lg">Buy Easy Squeeze Pegs at Biome →</a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-12 px-6 border-t border-navy-100 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto flex gap-4">
      <a href="/products/windy-conditions" class="text-sm font-semibold text-teal-500 hover:text-teal-700 underline